## ðŸ”§ TECHNICAL INTEGRATION NOTES

### Required Changes

#### App.jsx
```javascript
// Add imports
import AccessibilityControls from './components/AccessibilityControls'
import UpdateNotification from './components/UpdateNotification'
import './styles/accessibility.css'

// Add to render
<AccessibilityControls content={currentContent} />
<UpdateNotification />
```

#### AdminDashboard.jsx
```javascript
// Add imports
import AssetLibrary from './components/AssetLibrary'

// Add button to header
<button onClick={() => setShowAssetLibrary(true)}>
  Asset Library
</button>

// Add modal
{showAssetLibrary && <AssetLibrary onClose={() => setShowAssetLibrary(false)} />}
```

#### ModuleCreatorV2.jsx
```javascript
// Add imports
import ModuleImportExport from './components/ModuleImportExport'
import ModuleVersionControl from './components/ModuleVersionControl'
import PowerPointImporter from './components/PowerPointImporter'
import PDFImporter from './components/PDFImporter'
import MarkdownImporter from './components/MarkdownImporter'

// Add toolbar buttons
<button onClick={() => setShowImportExport(true)}>Import/Export</button>
<button onClick={() => setShowVersionControl(true)}>Version History</button>
```

#### Template Registry
```javascript
// Add to getTemplateComponent function
case 'branching': return BranchingScenario;
case 'codeplayground': return CodePlayground;
case 'model3d': return Model3DViewer;
case 'whiteboard': return VirtualWhiteboard;
case 'forum': return DiscussionForum;
```

